extendedInfo.description: 4 days of "AHA!" momentsNational Association of Elementary School PrincipalsThe National Conference of the Year -Best Practices for Better SchoolsThis summer, join some of the smartest thinkers in elementary school education and stay ahead of the dynamic changes taking place at the national level. With more than 100 sessions to choose from, this is where you'll find engaging speakers and like-minded colleagues eager to share solutions.Baltimore will be a magnet for the most inspired and motivated elementary school principals, assistant principals, teachers, superintendents, and experts in the nation. And that includes you!Great speakers.Great conference.Great location.App Keywords:principal, elementary school, training, Adam Saenz, Freeman Hrabowski, Baltimore
